info:
# topic
msg.topic must be "multiple"

# payload
msg.paylod contains array of nodeId objects
{"nodeId": "ns=1;s=NodeIdString"

name: 读取参数变量
数据分类
读取报警变量
func:
const AlarmSource = JSON.parse(msg.payload);   // 将消息负载中包含的 JSON 字符串解析为 JavaScript 对象
flow.set('AlarmSource', AlarmSource);          // 将对象保存至 Flow 上下文，以便后续使用

msg.topic = "multiple";                        // 设置消息主题为多重请求（如果需要）
msg.payload = Object.values(AlarmSource)       // 获取对象中所有属性值组成数组
    .flatMap(obj => obj.map(prop => prop.NodeId))  // 遍历每个属性并将其节点 ID 值添加到结果数组中
    .map(nodeId => ({ nodeId }));              // 根据 ID 值创建新对象构建最终结果

return msg;                                    // 返回处理后的消息对象

name: Charttemperatuur
format:
<html>
<iframe id="myFrame"  width="800" height="500" frameborder="0"></iframe>

<script>
//NOTE, more then one chart on a page, rename in the second and following 
//templates the "myframe" variable so that every template has a unique name.
(function(scope) {
    // watch msg object from Node-RED
    scope.$watch('msg', function(msg) {
        // new message received
        var x = document.getElementById('myFrame');
        x.setAttribute('src', msg.payload); 
        });
})(scope);
</script>
</html>
